# Utilify - Utility Bill Management System

**Live Site:** [https://b12a10-utility-management.web.app/home](https://b12a10-utility-management.web.app/home)

Utilify is a modern, user-friendly web application that simplifies paying utility bills ‚Äî electricity, gas, water, internet, and mobile ‚Äî all in one place. No queues, no hassle, just tap and pay.

---

## Features

- **One-Click Bill Payment** ‚Äì Pay any utility bill in under 30 seconds.
- **Current Month Only** ‚Äì Ensures accurate billing by restricting payments to the current month.
- **Secure Authentication** ‚Äì Firebase-powered login via Email/Password or Google Sign-In.
- **Protected Routes** ‚Äì Private access to bill details and payment using `PrivateRoute`.
- **Responsive Design** ‚Äì Built with Tailwind CSS and DaisyUI for seamless experience on mobile (5 cm / 2 in screens) and desktop.
- **Interactive UI** ‚Äì Hero carousel, category cards, recent bills grid, and smooth animations.
- **Real-time Data** ‚Äì Fetches bills from backend at `https://b12a10-utility-management-server.vercel.app/`.

---

